title: Ebro In The Morning - Swizz Beatz talks DMX + Big Knick Energy
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning.

In this episode, Swizz Beatz comes on the program to promote the DMX record Exodus (48:30), DJ Juan plays himself (38:00), Rosenberg talks about the NBA (33:00), and Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (12:45 & 44:00).

BTW Summer Jam is back...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
